entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have successfully rescued the fourth Imperial Officer from the Rebel Detainment Facility.
entries.journal_entry_description: Search the Rebel Detainment Facility for the next Imperial Officer being held prisoner.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Desert Trooper in combat and take his Desert Trooper Armor.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Get the disguise from Falen Buir
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Defeat some Prison Tracker Droids located in the main detention room.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Defeat some Prison Battle Droids located in the main detention room.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Defeat Prison Troopers located in the main detention room.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Search the main detention room located at the center of the Detention Facility. The pilot should be in one of the Eastern containment bays.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Give the officer the disguise you have.
